Finish the static method 'isSame' so that it takes two int[]arrays and returns true if they are the same(the length and the elements are exactly the same), otherwise, it returns false.

Example1:
int[]a={1,2,3};
int[]b={1,2,3};
isSame(a,b)=true;

Example2:
int[]a={1,2,3};
int[]b={1,2};
isSame(a,b)=false;

Example3:
int[]a={1,2,3};
int[]b={1,3,3};
isSame(a,b)=false;

